{"content": "I need to multiply 2a3 \u00d7 510 in base 11.\n\n**Step 1: Convert 2a3 (base 11) to base 10**\n- 2a3 = 2\u00d711\u00b2 + 10\u00d711\u00b9 + 3\u00d711\u2070\n- = 2\u00d7121 + 10\u00d711 + 3\u00d71\n- = 242 + 110 + 3\n- = 355\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Convert 510 (base 11) to base 10**\n- 510 = 5\u00d711\u00b2 + 1\u00d711\u00b9 + 0\u00d711\u2070\n- = 5\u00d7121 + 1\u00d711 + 0\n- = 605 + 11 + 0\n- = 616\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Multiply in base 10**\n- 355 \u00d7 616 = 218,680\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 4: Convert 218,680 back to base 11**\n- 218,680 \u00f7 11 = 19,880 R 0\n- 19,880 \u00f7 11 = 1,807 R 3\n- 1,807 \u00f7 11 = 164 R 3\n- 164 \u00f7 11 = 14 R 10 (a)\n- 14 \u00f7 11 = 1 R 3\n- 1 \u00f7 11 = 0 R 1\n\nReading remainders from bottom to top: 13a330\n\n**Answer: 13a330**", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 365, "completion_tokens": 398}